---
const navItems = [
	{ href: '#about', label: 'About' },
	{ href: '#fcm', label: 'Full Circle MUD' },
	{ href: '#other-work', label: 'Other Work' },
	{ href: '#stack', label: 'Tech Stack' },
	{ href: '#contact', label: 'Contact' },
];

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();

const siteTitle = 'Tim Baird — Software Developer · XRPL · AI/LLM';
const siteDescription =
	'Software developer building production XRPL and AI/LLM systems. Currently shipping Full Circle MUD — a live MMO with on-chain integration and LLM-driven content pipelines.';
const canonicalUrl = 'https://timbaird.com';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />

		<title>{siteTitle}</title>
		<meta name="description" content={siteDescription} />
		<link rel="canonical" href={canonicalUrl} />

		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />

		<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
		<meta property="og:title" content={siteTitle} />
		<meta property="og:description" content={siteDescription} />
		<meta property="og:url" content={canonicalUrl} />
		<!-- TODO: add og:image once typographic OG image is generated -->

		<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
		<meta name="twitter:title" content={siteTitle} />
		<meta name="twitter:description" content={siteDescription} />

		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			'@context': 'https://schema.org',
			'@type': 'Person',
			name: 'Tim Baird',
			alternateName: 'Timothy Baird',
			jobTitle: 'Software Developer',
			url: canonicalUrl,
			sameAs: [
				'https://github.com/timbaird',
				'https://github.com/fullcirclemud',
			],
			address: {
				'@type': 'PostalAddress',
				addressLocality: 'Melbourne',
				addressRegion: 'VIC',
				addressCountry: 'AU',
			},
		})} />

		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
	</head>

	<body>
		<nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary">
			<div class="nav-inner">
				<a href="#hero" class="nav-brand">Tim Baird</a>
				<ul class="nav-links">
					{navItems.map(item => (
						<li><a href={item.href} class="nav-link">{item.label}</a></li>
					))}
				</ul>
				<a href="https://app.timbaird.com" class="nav-portal">Client Login</a>
			</div>
		</nav>

		<main>
			<section id="hero" class="hero">
				<p class="hero-eyebrow">Software Developer · XRPL · AI/LLM</p>
				<h1 class="hero-name">Tim Baird</h1>
				<p class="hero-lede">
					I build production systems in <span class="accent">XRPL</span> and
					<span class="accent">AI/LLM</span>. Currently shipping
					<a href="https://fcmud.world">Full Circle MUD</a> — a live multiplayer
					game running on-chain transactions, multisig wallets, and
					LLM-driven content pipelines.
				</p>
				<div class="hero-cta">
					<a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/timbaird" class="btn btn-secondary">Personal GitHub</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/fullcirclemud" class="btn btn-secondary">FullCircleMUD GitHub</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="about" class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
				<div class="section-body">
					<p>
						Over a decade in software — building it, and teaching it. My most
						recent significant technical work is
						<a href="https://fcmud.world">Full Circle MUD</a>: a live game
						running XRPL multisig and NFT metadata, LLM pipelines with
						embeddings and vector stores, and a horizontally-scaled
						Evennia/Django backend.
					</p>
					<p>
						In addition to technical work, seven years teaching software
						engineering, database design, and programming at Swinburne
						University — which is where you really learn whether you
						understand something.
					</p>
					<p>
						Looking for <strong>XRPL or AI/LLM engineering roles</strong>. Open
						to senior crypto, Solidity, or general architecture work as
						stepping stones. Remote only. Currently Melbourne, globally
						mobile.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="fcm" class="section">
				<header class="section-title-row">
					<h2 class="section-title">Full Circle MUD</h2>
					<span class="section-eyebrow">Featured · Ongoing</span>
				</header>
				<div class="section-body">
					<p>
						A live multiplayer online game built on Evennia/Django, integrating
						XRPL blockchain and AI/LLM systems. Solo development. The
						architecture priority has been genuine decoupling — game subsystems
						communicate only through well-defined interfaces, enforced via
						bespoke Python libraries.
					</p>

					<ul class="tech-bullets">
						<li>
							<strong>XRPL on-chain integration.</strong> Multisig transactions,
							NFT metadata, supporting APIs for token operations.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>AI/LLM pipeline.</strong> OpenRouter and OpenAI API
							integration; embeddings stored in vector databases; a private
							LLM test-bot harness for automated dialogue regression testing.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Horizontal scaling framework.</strong> Engineered to
							distribute Evennia's single-threaded Twisted Reactor across
							multiple instances sharing a vertically-scaled Postgres backend.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Library architecture.</strong> Bespoke Python libraries
							enforce minimal coupling between game systems; each addressable
							as an independent concern.
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Operational tooling.</strong> XRPL wallet management
							interface (private repo) for internal use.
						</li>
					</ul>

					<div class="project-links">
						<a href="https://fcmud.world" class="link-pill">Live · fcmud.world</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/fullcirclemud" class="link-pill">
							github.com/fullcirclemud
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="other-work" class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Other Work</h2>
				<div class="section-body">
					<article class="project-card">
						<h3 class="project-name">Diploma of IT — Cloud &amp; Cyber Security</h3>
						<p class="project-meta">Bendigo Kangan Institute · Ongoing — expected completion July 2026</p>
						<p>
							End-to-end curriculum and assessment design from scratch for a
							Diploma of IT (Cloud &amp; Cyber Security), with a supporting
							course website built in <strong>Astro</strong>.
						</p>
						<p class="project-links-inline">
							<a href="https://github.com/Digital-Initiatives-Kangan-Institute/diploma-cloud-cyber-website">
								Website repo
							</a>
							·
							<a href="https://github.com/Digital-Initiatives-Kangan-Institute/diploma-cloud-cyber">
								Course repo
							</a>
						</p>
					</article>

					<article class="project-card">
						<h3 class="project-name">Personal projects</h3>
						<p class="project-meta">Ongoing</p>
						<p>
							Google Calendar API integration for the Go High Level CRM
							platform; OpenZeppelin-based Solidity smart contracts deployed on
							Polygon (FCM's original blockchain layer before the XRPL pivot);
							AI/LLM learning exercises and code samples created for students;
							additional projects in Oracle PL/SQL, C#, and JavaScript.
						</p>
						<p class="project-links-inline">
							<a href="https://github.com/timbaird">github.com/timbaird</a>
						</p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="stack" class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Tech Stack</h2>
				<div class="section-body">
					<p class="section-lede">
						Tools picked up as the work demanded. Most languages and
						frameworks are first principles in different costumes — I
						optimise for the problem, not framework loyalty.
					</p>
					<dl class="stack-grid">
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">Languages</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">
								Python · C# (.NET) · JavaScript · SQL (T-SQL, PL/SQL) · Solidity · Bash
							</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">Frameworks</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">Django · Evennia · ASP.NET · Astro</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">AI / LLM</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">
								OpenAI API · OpenRouter · vector databases · embeddings
							</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">Blockchain</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">
								XRPL · multisig · NFT metadata · EVM smart contracts
							</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">Cloud &amp; DevOps</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">AWS · Azure · CI/CD pipelines · Git</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">Databases</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">
								PostgreSQL · MS SQL Server · Oracle · vector stores
							</dd>
						</div>
						<div class="stack-cell">
							<dt class="stack-label">Architecture</dt>
							<dd class="stack-items">
								Loosely-coupled / decoupled systems · RESTful APIs · layered design
							</dd>
						</div>
					</dl>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="contact" class="section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Contact</h2>
				<div class="section-body">
					<p class="contact-intro">
						If you already have my resume, my direct email and phone are on
						it — use those. Otherwise, drop me a message via the form.
						Resume and referees available on request. (Keeping them off
						the public page protects both my direct contact and my
						referees' details from scrapers — Nigerian princes don't fill
						out forms.)
					</p>
					<div class="contact-form">
						<iframe
							src="https://links.timbaird.com/widget/form/DTfSKrqvOV6klM3azLGH"
							style="width:100%;min-height:520px;border:none;border-radius:6px"
							id="inline-DTfSKrqvOV6klM3azLGH"
							data-layout="{'id':'INLINE'}"
							data-trigger-type="alwaysShow"
							data-trigger-value=""
							data-activation-type="alwaysActivated"
							data-activation-value=""
							data-deactivation-type="neverDeactivate"
							data-deactivation-value=""
							data-form-name="timbaird.com-contact"
							data-height="507"
							data-layout-iframe-id="inline-DTfSKrqvOV6klM3azLGH"
							data-form-id="DTfSKrqvOV6klM3azLGH"
							title="timbaird.com-contact"
						></iframe>
						<script
							src="https://links.timbaird.com/js/form_embed.js"
							is:inline
						></script>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<footer class="footer">
			<p>© {currentYear} Tim Baird · All rights reserved</p>
		</footer>

		<style is:global>
			:root {
				--bg: #0f1117;
				--surface: #18191f;
				--surface-2: #1f2028;
				--text: #e8eaed;
				--text-muted: #9ca3af;
				--text-dim: #6b7280;
				--accent: #14b8a6;
				--accent-hover: #2dd4bf;
				--border: #2a2b34;
				--font-sans: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
					'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
				--font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, 'SFMono-Regular', Menlo,
					monospace;
				--content-width: 760px;
				--nav-height: 64px;
				--section-py: 5rem;
			}

			*,
			*::before,
			*::after {
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}

			html {
				background: var(--bg);
				color: var(--text);
				font-family: var(--font-sans);
				font-size: 16px;
				line-height: 1.65;
				-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
				-moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
				scroll-behavior: smooth;
				scroll-padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 1rem);
			}

			body {
				margin: 0;
				background: var(--bg);
				min-height: 100vh;
			}

			h1,
			h2,
			h3 {
				color: var(--text);
				line-height: 1.2;
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			a {
				color: var(--accent);
				text-decoration: none;
				border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
				transition: border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
			}

			a:hover {
				border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
			}

			strong {
				color: var(--text);
				font-weight: 600;
			}

			code {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.95em;
			}

			main {
				padding-top: var(--nav-height);
			}

			/* === Navigation === */

			.nav {
				position: fixed;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				right: 0;
				height: var(--nav-height);
				background: rgba(15, 17, 23, 0.85);
				backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
				-webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
				z-index: 100;
			}

			.nav-inner {
				max-width: 1100px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 0 1.5rem;
				height: 100%;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 2rem;
			}

			.nav-brand {
				color: var(--text);
				font-weight: 600;
				font-size: 1rem;
				border-bottom: none;
				letter-spacing: -0.01em;
			}

			.nav-brand:hover {
				color: var(--accent);
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.nav-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 1.5rem;
				margin-left: auto;
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
				margin-block: 0;
			}

			.nav-link {
				color: var(--text-muted);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.nav-link:hover {
				color: var(--text);
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.nav-portal {
				color: var(--text);
				border: 1px solid var(--border);
				border-radius: 999px;
				padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				letter-spacing: 0.01em;
				transition: border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
			}

			.nav-portal:hover {
				border-color: var(--accent);
				color: var(--accent);
			}

			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				.nav-links {
					display: none;
				}
				.nav-brand {
					margin-right: auto;
				}
			}

			/* === Hero === */

			.hero {
				max-width: var(--content-width);
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
			}

			.hero-eyebrow {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				color: var(--accent);
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}

			.hero-name {
				font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
				font-weight: 700;
				margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
				letter-spacing: -0.025em;
			}

			.hero-lede {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
				max-width: 60ch;
				line-height: 1.55;
			}

			.hero-lede .accent {
				color: var(--text);
				font-weight: 500;
			}

			.hero-lede a {
				color: var(--text);
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent);
			}

			.hero-lede a:hover {
				color: var(--accent);
			}

			.hero-cta {
				display: flex;
				gap: 0.75rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
			}

			/* === Buttons === */

			.btn {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.65rem 1.4rem;
				border-radius: 6px;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
				font-weight: 500;
				border: 1px solid transparent;
				border-bottom-width: 1px;
				transition: all 0.15s ease;
			}

			.btn:hover {
				border-bottom-width: 1px;
			}

			.btn-primary {
				background: var(--accent);
				color: var(--bg);
				border-color: var(--accent);
			}

			.btn-primary:hover {
				background: var(--accent-hover);
				border-color: var(--accent-hover);
			}

			.btn-secondary {
				background: transparent;
				color: var(--text);
				border-color: var(--border);
			}

			.btn-secondary:hover {
				border-color: var(--text-muted);
				color: var(--text);
			}

			/* === Sections === */

			.section {
				max-width: var(--content-width);
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: var(--section-py) 1.5rem;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
			}

			.section:last-of-type {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.section-title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				font-weight: 600;
				margin: 0 0 2rem;
			}

			.section-title-row {
				display: flex;
				align-items: baseline;
				justify-content: space-between;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				gap: 0.75rem;
				margin-bottom: 2rem;
			}

			.section-title-row .section-title {
				margin: 0;
			}

			.section-eyebrow {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				letter-spacing: 0.02em;
			}

			.section-body p {
				margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
			}

			.section-body p:last-child {
				margin-bottom: 0;
			}

			.section-lede {
				font-size: 1.05rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin: 0 0 2rem !important;
			}

			/* === Tech bullets === */

			.tech-bullets {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
			}

			.tech-bullets li {
				padding: 1rem 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
			}

			.tech-bullets li:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.tech-bullets strong {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.95em;
				color: var(--accent);
				font-weight: 500;
				display: block;
				margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
			}

			/* === Project links === */

			.project-links {
				display: flex;
				gap: 0.75rem;
				flex-wrap: wrap;
				margin-top: 1.5rem;
			}

			.link-pill {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
				border: 1px solid var(--border);
				border-radius: 999px;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				color: var(--text);
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
				transition: border-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
			}

			.link-pill:hover {
				border-color: var(--accent);
				color: var(--accent);
			}

			/* === Project cards === */

			.project-card {
				padding: 1.5rem 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
			}

			.project-card:first-child {
				padding-top: 0;
			}

			.project-card:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
				padding-bottom: 0;
			}

			.project-name {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
			}

			.project-meta {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.8rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
			}

			.project-links-inline {
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				margin-top: 0.75rem;
			}

			/* === Tech stack grid === */

			.stack-grid {
				margin: 0;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				gap: 0;
			}

			.stack-cell {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: 11rem 1fr;
				gap: 1rem;
				padding: 1rem 0;
				border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
				align-items: baseline;
			}

			.stack-cell:last-child {
				border-bottom: none;
			}

			.stack-label {
				font-family: var(--font-mono);
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--accent);
				font-weight: 500;
				margin: 0;
			}

			.stack-items {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 0.95rem;
			}

			@media (max-width: 600px) {
				.stack-cell {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					gap: 0.25rem;
				}
			}

			/* === Contact === */

			.contact-intro {
				font-size: 1rem;
				color: var(--text-muted);
				margin: 0 0 2rem;
				max-width: 60ch;
				line-height: 1.65;
			}

			.contact-form {
				margin: 0;
			}

			/* === Footer === */

			.footer {
				max-width: var(--content-width);
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 0.85rem;
				color: var(--text-dim);
				border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
			}

			.footer p {
				margin: 0;
			}
		</style>
	</body>
</html>
